data.description: Need multi-generational living, large spaces for entertaining or private areas for guests? Look no further than this spacious home nestled on two cul-de-sac lots totaling 2.54acres. Chef's kitchen with large island, custom cabinetry & dual pantries. Main level has 4 Bedroom 4.5 bathroom. Private owner's retreat has dual walk-in closets, bowl sinks, beautiful soaking tub & separate shower. Large dining, office/flex space, and living room with fireplace. Laundry room & unheated drop zone plus an additional unheated flex space. One main-level bath has accessible tub. Multiple doors lead to the enclosed porch and lower level covered patio. Downstairs, there are 2 additional bedrooms and 2 full baths. Great room with massive bar and fireplace for large gatherings or just relaxing. Lower level kitchen makes this ideal for secondary living space. Main level garage is currently converted to a media room but per sellers could be converted back easily. Located just minutes to I-85 and Hwy 74.
